<p rend="chapter">Uttaravinicchayo</p>

<p rend="subsubhead">Ganthārambhakathā</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="1"><hi rend="paranum">1</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Sabbasattuttamaṃ <pb ed="M" n="0.0305" /><pb ed="V" n="0.0269" /> dhīraṃ, vanditvā sirasā jinaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Dhammañcādhammaviddhaṃsaṃ, gaṇamaṅgaṇanāsanaṃ.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="2"><hi rend="paranum">2</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Yo mayā racito sāro, vinayassa vinicchayo;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Tassa dāni karissāmi, sabbānuttaramuttaraṃ.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="3"><hi rend="paranum">3</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Bhaṇato paṭhato payuñjato;</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Suṇato cintayato panuttaraṃ;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Paramaṃ abuddha buddhivaḍḍhanaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Vadato me niratā nibodhatha.</p>
